{"tid":2281484,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"習近平：要共建(大煉鋼) 共治(稱皇) 共享(割韭菜)","createTime":"2020-11-11T08:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T09:13:52.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3376554c0262b091a1924c0408b9baecae56b0f1","tid":2281484,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:19:03.000Z","msg":"習近平強調要落實總體國家安全觀<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平說，要落實總體國家安全觀，堅持共建共治共享方向，聚焦影響國家安全、社會安定、人民安寧的突出問題，深入推進市域社會治理現代化。<br />\n<br />\n習近平在平安中國建設工作會議指出，要深化平安創建活動，加強基層組織、基礎工作、基本能力建設，強調各級黨委及政府要加強對平安建設的組織領導，研究解決體制、機制及政策問題，切實肩負起促一方發展、保一方平安的政治責任。<br />\n<br />\n中央上星期發布十四五規劃及2035年遠景目標的建議，相較以往的五年規劃，今次在統籌發展和安全，建設高水平的平安中國方面，著墨較多。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2365779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2365779&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEdHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=9c8857fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2365779</a>"},{"pid":"30a7bd7cc0837d7581eaeb5aac12ecd1b07bd048","tid":2281484,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:20:51.000Z","msg":"篇嘢真係唔知up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f03b6ce56c1832c0e3e802fb6ecfdee986f125f","tid":2281484,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:00:41.000Z","msg":"簡單咁講<br />\n<br />\n習豬頭已做到2035年<br />\n<br />\n呢條友都廢事被人5年追一次數 <br />\n直接改成15年"},{"pid":"efb668a05c22ab1704b4d8d94675402a376b1f1e","tid":2281484,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:11:22.000Z","msg":"勁共X3?"},{"pid":"61e9c296c6e7f2fd016a565f8d2b25dff3e05e53","tid":2281484,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30a7bd7cc0837d7581eaeb5aac12ecd1b07bd048","tid":2281484,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:20:51.000Z","msg":"篇嘢真係唔知up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /